---
title: "US18a — Basic AI progress summary"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HistoryScreen (AI sheet)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SummariseProgress
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ProgressSummary
  A->>B: tap AI summary
  B->>C: call()
  C->>E: summariseProgress(range)
  alt summary returned
    E-->>C: ProgressSummary (text + model tag)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (ProgressSummary)
    B-->>A: summary, labelled "AI-assisted - not medical advice"
  else AI unavailable
    E-->>C: Exception
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: friendly error, retry
  end
  note over E: summariseProgress via AiGateway → summarise-progress Edge Function<br/>(OpenAI gpt-4o-mini, Gemini/stub fallback) - reads ended sessions server-side -<br/>basic tier = generic prose, Premium personalises (US36)
